ActCanada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Employment and Social Development of BRUCE SHIRREFF of Toronto, Ontario, to be director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basis, for a term of four years, in the place of Anne MacDonald.
